node.text:
Since I haven’t seen the track yet, I hit up the local @chaseelliott9 for some Atlanta Speedway advice. We’re gonna keep it low and consistent. Rights don’t matter! 🏁

@ktmusa @redbull @teamhendrick @supercrosslive @nascar

node.text:
Regardless of the person or job, we all experience good days and bad days on the clock, but I’m thankful to get to wake up and do what I love 🙌🏽

🎥 @didchain

node.text:
The Pacific Northwest fans were alive and thriving today 🔊. P6 OA at Washougal. Going to use this two week break to try and find that next step. 5 to go 💪🏽

@ktmusa @redbull @thormxofficial @bellhelmets @100percent_moto @alpinestarsmx @paradiseautos @iamspecialized 📸 @align.with.us

node.text:
Sums up my weekend 🤷🏽‍♂️. Sixth in the first moto and kissed wheels on my my way to a big one in moto 2. It’s racing and shit happens. We’ll be back next weekend for more 💪🏽

@ktmusa @redbull @thormxofficial @bellhelmets @100percent_moto @alpinestarsmx @paradiseautos @iamspecialized
